  "contentHtml": "\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <p><img src=\"https://health.economictimes.indiatimes.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/et-default-user.svg\" alt=\"Online Bureau\">\n                                            \n                                        </p>\n                                                                        \n                                                                                    <ul>\n                                                                                                    <li>\n                                                                                                                                                                            <a>Online Bureau</a>\n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                                                                                                            </li>\n                                                                                                                                                    <li><a href=\"/agency/88675629/ETHealthWorld\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ETHealthWorld</a></li>\n                                                                                            </ul>\n                                                                                <ul>\n                                                                                            <li>Updated On Jul 21, 2026 at 07:15 PM IST</li>\n                                                                                                                                </ul>\n                                    \n                                                                            \n                                                                        \n                                \n                                \n\n                    <!-- Display video article in news article for the custom next story -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Modifying the body placing embeds,promoslots,related etc.-->\n                                        <figure><img src=\"/images/default.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure><p>Gurugram: Agilus Diagnostic, a subsidiary of <a href=\"/tag/fortis+healthcare\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Fortis Healthcare</a> group has appointed Vijender Singh as its Managing Director and Chief Executive Officer.Singh will succeed Dr Anand K who resigned from the post to pursue opportunities outside the organisation after being associated with the company for nearly six years, Agilus said.Prior to joining Agilus, Singh served as Chairman and Managing Director of Diagnum Healthcare, where he focused on strategic growth, governance and business development.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>He has previously held various leadership positions including Group CEO, Metropolis Healthcare, Healthians and spent a decade with Dr. Lal PathLab.</p>\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        <p>“We are delighted to welcome Vijender Singh as the Managing Director &amp; Chief Executive Officer of <a href=\"/tag/agilus+diagnostics\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Agilus Diagnostics</a>. Vijender Singh brings extensive experience in building and scaling diagnostic businesses, driving operational excellence and creating sustainable value across healthcare organisations,” said Dr Ashutosh Raghuvanshi, Managing Director &amp; Chief Executive Officer, Fortis Healthcare Limited and Chairman, Agilus Diagnostics.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>“As the diagnostics landscape continues to evolve, we believe his leadership will further strengthen our capabilities, accelerate innovation, enhance customer experience and reinforce Agilus’ position as one of India’s most trusted diagnostic brands,” Raghuvanshi added.                    </p><!-- Category Most Read Placement -->\n                                                                    \n                                                                \n                                <ul>\n                                                                            <!-- <li>By <span>Online Bureau</span>,</li> -->\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <li>By\n                                                                                            <a>Online Bureau</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                        , \n                                                                                    </li>\n                                                                        <li><a href=\"/agency/88675629/ETHealthWorld\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ETHealthWorld</a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <!-- <li> Updated On Jul 21, 2026 at 07:15 PM IST</li> -->\n                                    <li>Published On Jul 21, 2026 at 12:25 PM IST</li>\n                                    <!-- <li class=\"desktop-view\">1 min read</li> -->\n                                </ul>\n                            \n                                        \n\n                    \n\n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n                                            \n                               